  <!-- ── Services Page ───────────────────────────────────── -->
  <item>
    <title>Services</title>
    <dc:creator>milo</dc:creator>
    <content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h2>What I can help with</h2>

<p>I work as an embedded design-engineer &mdash; usually for six to twelve weeks, with a clear outcome agreed up front. Here&rsquo;s how that typically breaks down.</p>

<h3>Product Design &amp; Systems</h3>
<p>Design systems, component libraries, and full product flows that stay consistent as teams scale. I build the Figma files <em>and</em> the React components &mdash; no translation layer required.</p>

<h3>Front-End Engineering</h3>
<p>Production-grade interfaces in React, TypeScript, Next.js, or vanilla HTML/CSS. Pixel-perfect, performant, and accessible out of the box. I write the code I design.</p>

<h3>Brand &amp; Visual Identity</h3>
<p>For teams that need more than a logo. I create visual systems &mdash; type scales, colour palettes, motion language &mdash; that hold up from pitch deck to product UI.</p>

<h3>Research &amp; Strategy</h3>
<p>User interviews, competitive audits, and information architecture. I do the thinking before the building, so we ship the right thing the first time.</p>

<h3>Pricing</h3>
<p>Pricing is per engagement rather than hourly &mdash; typically $18&ndash;45k depending on scope and shape. I try to quote tightly and won&rsquo;t take a project I don&rsquo;t think will succeed.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
    <excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[Product design, front-end engineering, brand identity, and research — all from one desk.]]></excerpt:encoded>
